    {
      "text": "Luxor 2 is a puzzle video game developed by MumboJumbo. First released in 2006, it is the sequel to the original Luxor, which was released in 2005. The title can be played online at several different sites, and is also available for purchase for Microsoft Windows and Mac OS X.\nThe game's console debut was in April 2007, with its release on Xbox 360 via Xbox Live Arcade. The game was removed from App Store in 2024, as with all other Luxor games released (except Luxor Evolved).",
